    <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl text-white mb-4">Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    <div class="rounded-xl border border-dashed border-white/15 p-6 text-white/40 text-sm italic mb-8">
      TODO — Paste your full Terms of Use here. Generate at{' '}
      <a href="https://app.termly.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-white/60">termly.io</a>
      {' '}(free plan). Cover: acceptable use, no clinical reliance disclaimer (tools are for administrative/operational use only, not clinical decision-making), intellectual property, limitation of liability, governing law (Cameroon / OHADA).
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-xl bg-amber-500/[0.05] border border-amber-500/20 p-5 text-sm text-amber-200/70 leading-relaxed">
